          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with the juice of the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and 1 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and half the <strong>mint leaves</strong> (save the rest for later!) &ndash; this is your <strong>lemony dressing</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1439.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Gently wash and pat the <strong>lamb's lettuce</strong> dry</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>lamb's l</strong><strong>ettuce</strong>,<strong> courgette ribbons</strong>, <strong>cooked spelt</strong> and<strong> remaining mint leaves</strong> to a very large mixing bowl</p>\r\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, pour over the <strong>lemony dressing</strong> and give everything a good old mix up</p>\r\n<p>Remove the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> from the oven and slice it finely</p>",
      "order": 7,
